      <title>爆炸致美国工人受伤后，ADM 被指控行为不当、缺乏安全检查</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/adm-accused-misconduct-lack-safety-inspections-after-explosion-hurt-us-worker-2024-10-17/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据针对阿彻丹尼尔斯米德兰公司提起的诉讼，该公司多年来故意未能对其谷物设备的安全系统进行测试和维护，导致去年发生爆炸，导致一名工人自焚并陷入昏迷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/adm-accused-misconduct-lack-safety-inspections-after-explosion-hurt-us-worker-2024-10-17/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 20:27:54 GMT</pubDate>
